I"x<h2 id="set-static-ip-address">Set Static IP Address</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ifconfig eth0 &lt;<span class="nv">$IP</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> netmask &lt;<span class="nv">$NETMASK</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> broadcast &lt;<span class="nv">$BROADCAST</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="change-mac-address">Change MAC Address</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ifconfig eth0 hw ether &lt;<span class="nv">$MAC_ADDRESS</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="add-alias-interface">Add Alias Interface</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ifconfig eth0:0 &lt;<span class="nv">$ALIAS_IP</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="enable-promiscuous-mode">Enable Promiscuous Mode</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>ifconfig eth0 promisc
</code></pre></div></div>

